column1: #  pval_perm_SmallestpQTL: Permutation-adjusted p-value corresponding to the top pQTL variant (with the smallest nominal p-value) for each protein.
# pval_nominal_threshold: The nomila pvalue threshold used to determine significant SNP_protein associations within each protein.
#  qval_protein: Protein-level FDR estimate derived from Storey's q-value method for multiple testing correction across proteins.
